The '''New Cov Biomolecule Company''' was a leading harvesting and exporting company of naturally occurring biomolecules that were indigenous to [[New Cov/Legends|New Cov]] from otherwise toxic plants and animals. These molecules had numerous applications galaxy-wide in medicine, industry, and military projects, and were often the objective of raids. The company was headquartered in [[Ilic]] on New Cov.

